CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1941, pg. 12 reads: "National Officers, Delegates And Visitors To Debs About Town Confab In Pittsburgh"...In the photos top, left to right; Dorothy James, Cleveland; Lucille Johnson, Columbus; Jean Wright, Columbus; Eleanor Trott, Boston; Pauline Stewart, Columbus...- Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Debs About Town members Dorothy James, Lucille Johnson, Jean Wright, Eleanor Trott, and Pauline Stewart posed in front of Loendi Club porch
